cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.CY 

This paper primarily focuses on privacy and security concerns related to data usage, which falls under the category of "cs.CR" (Cryptography and Security). The proposed system also leverages blockchain technology, which is commonly used in "cs.DC" (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and "cs.DB" (Databases) sub-categories. The use of smart contracts and trusted execution environment also involves software engineering concepts, which can be categorized under "cs.SE" (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper discusses the societal impacts of data privacy, which can be related to "cs.CY" (Computers and Society).
